des:
Ask for weird Facts, and learn about the wierd and the wonderful.

weird Facts provides fun the whole family can enjoy and is guaranteed to make you smarter (and weirder).

To start, just say "Alexa, launch weird Facts" or "Alexa, open weird Facts" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
